                         THREADING MODEL
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Main Thread (process_downloads):
├─ [Daemon]  display_progress()
│            └─ Updates 4 slot statuses every 0.5s (can exit anytime)
│
├─ [Non-Daemon] download_worker(slot_id=0)
├─ [Non-Daemon] download_worker(slot_id=1)
├─ [Non-Daemon] download_worker(slot_id=2)
├─ [Non-Daemon] download_worker(slot_id=3)
│              └─ Processes queue items sequentially (one per worker)
│
└─ [Main]  Monitor loop
           └─ Waits for queue empty + active_downloads=0


Synchronization:
├─ self.lock (threading.Lock)
│   └─ Protects: active_downloads counter
│
└─ self.slot_lock (threading.Lock)
    └─ Protects: slot_status[] (display updates)


