                         RETRY STRATEGY
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Conditions Triggering Retry:
├─ Size mismatch detected (incomplete download)
│   └─ wget -c automatically resumes partial file
│
├─ Network errors (codes 1, 2, 3, 4)
│   └─ Full retry with fresh download
│
├─ Timeout errors (code 124 or -9)
│   └─ Full retry with fresh download
│
└─ Other transient failures (WGET_ERROR_1, etc.)
    └─ Full retry with fresh download

Non-Retryable Failures:
├─ Permission denied (code 5)
├─ Protocol error (code 6)
├─ Cannot verify file size (no expected size available)
└─ Other persistent errors


Default Retry Configuration:
├─ max_retries = 3
└─ retry_wait_time = 5 seconds


